  "3310260": {
    "name": "Accolade Sports Collection (QUByte Classics)",
    "steam_appid": 3310260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/4d1c655024268cc36716e0e13c58e3c0.avif?t=1752782136\" width=616 height=227 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过《Accolade 体育系列》重温复古体育游戏的黄金时代！从传奇的棒球到令人热血沸腾的街头篮球，再到史诗般的冬季和夏季挑战，本合集包含 5 款令人难忘的经典游戏！怀旧的画面和原汁原味的游戏玩法，让您有机会回到过去，体验 90 年代最精彩的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的复古游戏体验，玩家可以轻松选择不同的游戏，包括保存状态、过滤器选项、手册等功能！ 轻松获得各种体育体验，同时享受现代增强功能带来的便利。每款游戏的机制都得到了保留，以保持原汁原味的感觉！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冬季挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在八项最刺激、最具挑战性的冬季运动项目中体验竞技的快感。每次游戏，您都会促使自己跑得更快、跳得更远：雪橇、下坡滑雪、越野滑雪、雪橇、速度滑冰、大回转、冬季两项和跳台滑雪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/dff5a76333daf559bb03924dafc6732d.poster.avif?t=1752782136\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/dff5a76333daf559bb03924dafc6732d.webm?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/dff5a76333daf559bb03924dafc6732d.mp4?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >夏季挑战赛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一生的训练归结为一个瞬间。来自全球各地速度最快、最强壮、技术最娴熟的冠军们齐聚一座伟大的城市，决出谁是最优秀的选手。在冬季挑战赛的续集中，夏季版包括 8 个令人难以置信的项目：皮划艇、射箭、400 米栏、跳高、撑杆跳、马术、标枪和自行车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/37b45e6833fb0b7d389306cc9627b8e5.poster.avif?t=1752782136\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/37b45e6833fb0b7d389306cc9627b8e5.webm?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/37b45e6833fb0b7d389306cc9627b8e5.mp4?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >硬式棒球</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棒球传奇再现！准备好重温这款定义了一代棒球模拟器的游戏所带来的快感吧。该游戏最初于上世纪 80 和 90 年代推出，如今带着赢得全球粉丝青睐的经典魅力回归。Hardball！》拥有引人入胜的游戏玩法、迷人的复古画面和浓浓的怀旧情怀，无论是想重温辉煌时刻的老玩家，还是喜欢经典游戏风格的新玩家，都能在游戏中找到乐趣。组建你的球队，挑战对手，体验这款至今仍是全垒打的游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本地多人游戏模式中挑战好友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/d1a5f8ab26b1e7a2470e7dc58d6105b4.poster.avif?t=1752782136\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/d1a5f8ab26b1e7a2470e7dc58d6105b4.webm?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/d1a5f8ab26b1e7a2470e7dc58d6105b4.mp4?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >硬式棒球 II</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >硬式棒球 II》是棒球模拟器系列的经典之作！该游戏最初于上世纪 90 年代推出，续集以当时先进的图形、精致的游戏和深度再次重新定义了这一类型游戏，令体育迷大呼过瘾。管理策略，完善技能，享受虚拟棒球体验，这将继续成为复古游戏中的标杆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双人本地多人模式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/6bb9f4141e0c997efd3b927eb9394e7b.poster.avif?t=1752782136\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/6bb9f4141e0c997efd3b927eb9394e7b.webm?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/6bb9f4141e0c997efd3b927eb9394e7b.mp4?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >篮球、闭嘴和果酱！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从未见过的球场动作！进入《Hoops Shut Up and Jam! 没有硬性规定，没有任何限制--这是原始、激烈、有趣的篮球运动，其灵感来自于当时篮球明星的独特风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本地多人合作模式中向好友寻求帮助，或在一对一本地多人模式中挑战最大的对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/06b22907f1c4d88577055dccb5ffe76c.poster.avif?t=1752782136\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/06b22907f1c4d88577055dccb5ffe76c.webm?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310260/extras/06b22907f1c4d88577055dccb5ffe76c.mp4?t=1752782136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
